commit.message:
Fix typo 'exapnded' to 'expanded'

2018-08-23  Giuliano Belinassi  <giuliano.belinassi@usp.br>

gcc/
	* genmatch.c (parser::parse_operation): Fix typo 'exapnded'
	to 'expanded'.
